This software ("the Plugin") is copyrighted by sonamika-jp ("the Author").
By using the Plugin, you agree to the following terms.

1. Permitted
   - Installing and running the compiled file (JAR) of the Plugin on a
     Minecraft server that you operate.
   - Changing settings using the provided configuration files.
   - Reporting bugs and submitting code improvement suggestions to the
     official repository (via GitHub Issues / Pull Requests, etc.).

2. Prohibited
   - Redistributing, reposting, or providing the Plugin (including source
     code and JAR) to third parties, whether free of charge or for a fee.
   - Modifying the Plugin without the Author's permission and publishing or
     distributing such modified or derivative versions.
   - Creating or publishing other software that incorporates the Plugin or
     any part of it.
   - Selling the Plugin, distributing it for a fee, or any other commercial use.
   - Removing or altering the copyright notice.

3. Contributions
   - Code improvement suggestions (e.g., Pull Requests) are welcome. Whether
     to adopt them is at the Author's discretion.
   - If a submitted contribution is adopted into the Plugin, it will be
     treated as part of the Plugin under the terms of this License.
   - Publishing or distributing a modified version independently, beyond the
     scope of submitting a suggestion, is prohibited under Section 2.

4. Disclaimer
   - The Plugin is provided "as is", without warranty of any kind, express or
     implied. The Author shall not be liable for any damages arising from the
     use of or inability to use the Plugin.

5. Reservation of Rights
   - All rights not expressly granted in this License are reserved by the Author.
   - The Author may change the terms of this License without prior notice.

